This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with depth estimation from multiple images. It may also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it discusses the use of a monocular camera for dense mapping. Additionally, the paper uses a neural network for depth estimation, which suggests it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper may also belong to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it deals with generating depth maps.
